review_data: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2021
name: Trinity
title: Good Granola
review: I have never had a "soft granola" before.This granola is not crunchy or hard; rather it like granola before you bake it.I like it and it is easier on my teeth to boot.It is good with yogurt and I think would be good on ice cream. It tastes like and has the consistency oatmeal chocolate chip cookie dough. I eat a low carb/keto diet and this fits in perfectly. The portion is reasonable for the carbs.Update: I did not find any identifiable chocolate chips in this granola although I do taste a bit of chocolate.

title: This the BEST!
review: Absolutely the BEST granola I have ever had and I have tried quite a few. Trying to find sugar free because of diabetes and low carbs for dietary reasons this is a real find. Ordered one the first time ordered three this time! Great on top of yogurt!

title: Not what I expected, but I dig it!
review: This is pretty alright stuff… but you must like coconut flavor, the coconut is strong in this one. It’s not crunchy, at all. Chewy, chocolaty, coconuty goodness, weighing in at one net carb. This is part of my monthly Subscibe & Save.
